{"tid":1668410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"送中條例一早講明死刑罪行唔會移交，陳同佳根本送唔送中都無影響，港共呢次抽錯水","createTime":"2019-10-22T03:21:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T05:23:40.000Z","uid":51271,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"21d0e4f2d3f093bef2ce0c9b368c2affa18684e1","tid":1668410,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T03:21:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E6%9D%8E%E5%AE%B6%E8%B6%85%EF%BC%9A%E5%A6%82%E8%A9%B2%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%E5%9F%B7%E8%A1%8C%E6%AD%BB%E5%88%91%E3%80%80%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E7%A7%BB%E4%BA%A4-171731\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25B6%2585%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%25A6%2582%25E8%25A9%25B2%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%259F%25B7%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E5%2588%2591%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E4%25BA%25A4-171731&d=kAMrkm0lh8tAzahNx%2FKaSEYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=aba35b02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E6%9D%8E%E5%AE%B6%E8%B6%85%EF%BC%9A%E5%A6%82%E8%A9%B2%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%E5%9F%B7%E8%A1%8C%E6%AD%BB%E5%88%91%E3%80%80%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E7%A7%BB%E4%BA%A4-171731</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港正苦你記唔記得五月果時你講乜</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n【逃犯條例】李家超：如該國會執行死刑 港府不會移交 <br />\n<strong>2019-05-07 </strong><br />\n政府今午就逃犯條例修例召開記者會。保安局長李家超指，香港每一個人都應努力令台灣殺人案疑犯面對法律制裁，政府是為了伸張正義而一直努力推動修例。至於被問及死刑不移交的相關事宜，李家超解釋，港府會保證移交人士不會被判死刑，或被判死刑後不會確實執行，才會同意移交，強調相關原則屬國際做法。"},{"pid":"4a7e7932f13718514f940bcd9a32331baf3aeca5","tid":1668410,"uid":50873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T03:24:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9c041aa3eefd43b965e90ddee9d852e0fc4b6b0","tid":1668410,"uid":60057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T03:25:03.000Z","msg":"雖然想同意你...不過「港府會保證移交人士不會被判死刑，或被判死刑後不會確實執行，才會同意移交，強調相關原則屬國際做法。」<br />\n<br />\n即係話如果陳同佳呢個例係要台灣答應唔會判死刑，或者就算判死刑都唔會執行先肯移交"},{"pid":"240863bf5a6344b057b7aefcfcc2f8035c4fb144","tid":1668410,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T03:26:11.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"b46a887baaaab9762c02a369f7eeab23a492a7fc","tid":1668410,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T03:26:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />林鄭:根據唔同既時勢會有唔同考量 依然保持初心"},{"pid":"01898ca3a8db32e38d2a144c03b8b0e5b237bae6","tid":1668410,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a9c041aa3eefd43b965e90ddee9d852e0fc4b6b0","tid":1668410,"uid":60057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T03:25:03.000Z","msg":"雖然想同意你...不過「港府會保證移交人士不會被判死刑，或被判死刑後不會確實執行，才會同意移交，強調相關原則屬國際做法。」<br />\n<br />\n即係話如果陳同佳呢個例係要台灣答應唔會判死刑，或者就算判死刑都唔會執行先肯移交"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T03:27:39.000Z","msg":"司法獨立，政府點可能代法庭判"},{"pid":"726550e0f4c6aecc430b1e3fdf84d2ee808c5b7d","tid":1668410,"uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"01898ca3a8db32e38d2a144c03b8b0e5b237bae6","tid":1668410,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a9c041aa3eefd43b965e90ddee9d852e0fc4b6b0","tid":1668410,"uid":60057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T03:25:03.000Z","msg":"雖然想同意你...不過「港府會保證移交人士不會被判死刑，或被判死刑後不會確實執行，才會同意移交，強調相關原則屬國際做法。」<br />\n<br />\n即係話如果陳同佳呢個例係要台灣答應唔會判死刑，或者就算判死刑都唔會執行先肯移交"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T03:27:39.000Z","msg":"司法獨立，政府點可能代法庭判"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T03:29:59.000Z","msg":"加拿大掟賴昌星過去都講明唔